text: Tapar'inle bhanidinus ki he yahudi ra isa'iharu! Ke timiharule hamisita yasakarana satruta gariraheka chau ki hamile allahamathi ra juna (kitaba) hamila'i pradana gari'eko cha ra juna (kitaba) aghi pradana gariyo, tyasamathi astha rakhdachaum? Ra yasa karana ki timiharumadhye dherai jaso uddanda ra ullanghanakari chan
